Package: ripserr
Type: Package
Title: Calculate Vietoris-Rips Persistent Homology
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Raoul", "Wadhwa", email = "raoulwadhwa@gmail.com", role = c("cre", "aut")),
    person("Jacob", "Scott", role = "aut"))
Description: Provides a wrapper for Ulrich Bauer's
    C++ Ripser library for calculating Vietoris-Rips persistent homology. When
    integrated using Rcpp, ripserr can be used seamlessly within R to calculate
    persistent homology within topological data analysis pipelines.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.3)
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.0.1
SystemRequirements: C++11
URL: https://github.com/rrrlw/ripserr
BugReports: https://github.com/rrrlw/ripserr/issues
